h3. GET
{{get.parameters}} has {{issue_id}}, but it&#x27;s already present in {{parameters}}. So it should be removed.

h3. POST
{{post.parameters}} has {{issue_id}}, but it&#x27;s already present in {{parameters}}. So it should be removed.

